---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="The Lifestyle â€” Playa Venao Living" description="Discover life in Playa Venao: world-class surfing, yoga retreats, jungle waterfalls, and a vibrant international community on Panama's Pacific coast.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src="/images/lifestyle/01-surfers-walking-to-ocean.jpeg" alt="Surfers walking to the ocean at Playa Venao" class="h-full w-full object-cover" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/50 via-black/30 to-black/60"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 text-center lg:px-8 py-32">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ocean-300">The Lifestyle</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
        This Is What Living Feels Like
      </h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
        Surf, yoga, jungle waterfalls, beach bonfires, and a community that feels like family. Playa Venao is not a destination. It is a way of life.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Surfing -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ocean-600">Surf Culture</p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
            The Best Waves in Panama
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Playa Venao is Panama's undisputed surf capital. The crescent-shaped bay catches swell from multiple directions, producing consistent waves year-round that work for everyone from first-time surfers to seasoned riders looking for powerful barrels.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            The water is warm all year, hovering around 27-29 degrees Celsius. Board shorts and a rash guard are all you need. Surf schools and board rentals line the beach, and the vibe is supportive and communal. Whether you surf every day or are just learning, the ocean is your backyard.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="rounded-xl bg-ocean-50 p-4">
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-ocean-700">365</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">Days of waves per year</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-xl bg-ocean-50 p-4">
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-ocean-700">27-29&deg;C</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">Water temperature</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-xl bg-ocean-50 p-4">
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-ocean-700">All Levels</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">Beginner to advanced</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-xl bg-ocean-50 p-4">
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-ocean-700">Walking</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">Distance from apartments</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <img src="/images/lifestyle/04-surfer-action-wave.jpeg" alt="Surfer riding a wave at Playa Venao" class="rounded-xl object-cover h-64 w-full" />
          <img src="/images/lifestyle/02-surfer-panama-flag-board.jpeg" alt="Surfer with Panama flag surfboard" class="rounded-xl object-cover h-64 w-full" />
          <img src="/images/lifestyle/06-surfer-girls-walking.jpeg" alt="Surfer girls walking on the beach" class="rounded-xl object-cover h-64 w-full col-span-2" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Nature & Wildlife -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-sand-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <img src="/images/lifestyle/01-waterfall-rocks.jpeg" alt="Waterfall in the jungle near Playa Venao" class="rounded-xl object-cover h-72 w-full col-span-2" />
          <img src="/images/lifestyle/02-creek-forest.jpeg" alt="Creek running through tropical forest" class="rounded-xl object-cover h-48 w-full" />
          <img src="/images/lifestyle/03-mother-child-beach-walk.jpeg" alt="Mother and child walking on the beach" class="rounded-xl object-cover h-48 w-full" />
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ocean-600">Nature & Wildlife</p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
            Where the Jungle Meets the Sea
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            The Azuero Peninsula is a biodiversity hotspot. Just minutes from the beach, you will find jungle waterfalls cascading over ancient rocks, forest creeks that invite you to swim, and trails that wind through canopies alive with tropical birds, howler monkeys, and iguanas.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            The coast itself is equally spectacular. From June to November, humpback whales migrate through the Pacific waters just offshore. Sea turtles nest on the beaches between June and December, and you can witness hatchlings make their way to the ocean under the stars.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-ocean-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              Whale watching (June - November)
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-ocean-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              Sea turtle nesting season (June - December)
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-ocean-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              Jungle waterfalls and hiking trails
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-ocean-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              Tropical birds, monkeys, and marine life
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-ocean-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              Horseback riding on the beach
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Yoga & Wellness -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ocean-600">Yoga & Wellness</p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
            Breathe. Move. Be.
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Playa Venao has become a magnet for wellness seekers. Several yoga retreats and studios operate in the area, offering everything from morning vinyasa flows on the beach to multi-week immersive retreats. The natural setting amplifies everything: sunrise meditation with ocean waves as your soundtrack, outdoor classes surrounded by tropical greenery, and a community that values mindfulness as much as adventure.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Beyond yoga, you will find massage therapists, health-conscious restaurants, organic food options, and a general culture of well-being that permeates daily life in Playa Venao. This is a place where taking care of yourself feels natural, not forced.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/images/lifestyle/02-yoga-outdoor-class.jpeg" alt="Outdoor yoga class near the beach" class="rounded-xl object-cover h-96 w-full" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Community & Food -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-sand-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <img src="/images/lifestyle/01-beach-football-night.jpeg" alt="Beach football game at night" class="rounded-xl object-cover h-56 w-full" />
          <img src="/images/lifestyle/07-surfers-celebrating.jpeg" alt="Surfers celebrating together" class="rounded-xl object-cover h-56 w-full" />
          <img src="/images/lifestyle/05-father-child-sunset-surf.jpeg" alt="Father and child at sunset with surf" class="rounded-xl object-cover h-56 w-full col-span-2" />
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ocean-600">Food & Community</p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
            Friends You Have Not Met Yet
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            The Playa Venao community is what keeps people coming back. Beach football under the lights, sunset gatherings, impromptu barbecues, and surf sessions that turn strangers into friends. The mix of locals, expats, and travelers creates a diverse, open-minded, and genuinely warm social fabric.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            The food scene is growing too. From beachside ceviche stands to restaurants serving international cuisine, there is no shortage of good eating. Fresh seafood, tropical fruits, and Panamanian specialties like sancocho and patacones are staples. Several restaurants and cafes cater to health-conscious eaters with plant-based and organic options.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Activities -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ocean-600">Activities</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
          Never a Dull Moment
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-14 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {[
          'Surfing & Bodyboarding',
          'Yoga & Meditation',
          'Snorkeling & Diving',
          'Jungle Hiking',
          'Waterfall Visits',
          'Horseback Riding',
          'Beach Football',
          'Whale Watching',
          'Sea Turtle Tours',
          'Fishing',
          'Stand-Up Paddleboarding',
          'Sunset Photography',
        ].map(activity => (
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-ocean-50 p-5 text-center hover:bg-ocean-100 transition-colors">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ocean-800">{activity}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Day in the Life -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-ocean-900 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ocean-300">A Day in the Life</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
          Your Average Tuesday in Playa Venao
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-8">
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-20 text-right">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-ocean-300">6:00 AM</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Wake up to the sound of waves. Step onto your terrace with a coffee and watch the sunrise paint the ocean gold. The air is warm and salty.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-20 text-right">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-ocean-300">7:00 AM</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Morning surf session. The tide is right and the waves are clean. You share the lineup with a handful of friendly faces. An hour of pure flow.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-20 text-right">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-ocean-300">8:30 AM</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Rinse off at the pool, grab a fresh smoothie bowl from the cafe nearby. Sit under a palm tree and plan your day.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-20 text-right">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-ocean-300">9:30 AM</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Open your laptop from the comfort of your apartment. Starlink is humming, and you join a video call with your team across three time zones.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-20 text-right">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-ocean-300">12:30 PM</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Lunch break. Walk to the beach for fresh ceviche and a cold beer. Check the waves -- maybe sneak in a quick session.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-20 text-right">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-ocean-300">2:00 PM</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Back to work for the afternoon. Close up a few hours of focused deep work while the afternoon breeze flows through the apartment.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-20 text-right">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-ocean-300">5:00 PM</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Yoga class on the beach as the sun starts to lower. Stretch, breathe, and let the day's work dissolve into the sand.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-20 text-right">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-ocean-300">6:30 PM</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Sunset from the pool deck. Someone brought a guitar. The sky turns orange, then purple. You realize this is just a Tuesday.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">This Could Be Your Life</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        Playa Venao Living puts all of this at your doorstep. Modern apartments, community pool, and a lifestyle that most people only dream about.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/#residences" class="w-full sm:w-auto rounded-lg bg-ocean-600 px-8 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-ocean-500 transition-colors">
          Explore Residences
        </a>
        <a href="/#contact" class="w-full sm:w-auto rounded-lg border-2 border-ocean-600 px-8 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-ocean-700 hover:bg-ocean-50 transition-colors">
          Get in Touch
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
